name: The Only People For Me Are The Mad Ones
description: Quote from Jack Kerouac on his autobiographical novel "On The Road", 1957. Some think that this highly poetic segment was the original inspiration for the speech on the famous first "Think Different" commercial from TBWA\Chiat\Day for Apple, aired in 1997. Technical data: typeset with Adobe Illustrator, Eurostile Bold Extended converted into curves. PNG file, 3784x3484px. First version 11 March 2015, resized and enhanced, NFT originally released as HeN OBJKT 39327 on 19 April 2021.
